CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 1957, pg. 3 reads: "Carnegie Tech Graduates - Catherine J. Ellison, Bachelor of Science; William D. McCullough of Newark, N.J. Master of Science in Industrial Administration; and Alma McCloud Evans, Bachelor of Science."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Carnegie Tech Graduates Catherine J. Ellison, William D. McCullough, and Alma McCloud Evans, posed in interior with dark curtains and striped sofa
